  <title>U.S. ZIP Code Points</title>
  <abstract>U.S. ZIP Code Points represents the five-digit U.S. ZIP Code areas as points, plus all ZIP Codes that have no associated area such as post office box ZIP Codes and single site ZIP Codes (government, building, or large volume customer).

U.S. ZIP Code Points provides ZIP Code, postal name, type, population, and area for the ZIP Code locations in the United States.</abstract>
